utral bottomup portfolio construction process creates increased opportunity for more consistent longterm returns by not depending on the growth and value cycles of the share market macquarie australian small companies fund seeking exposure to the big opportunities in small companies aims to invest in a diversified selection of some of the fastestgrowing australian companies give your clients the potential for consistent returns capital growth and some income our investment team identifies potentially attractive value and growth stocks through proprietary quantitative screening and an intense fundamental research process about international shares most of the worlds largest and most successful companies list on exchanges outside australia also asias emerging markets provide exciting growth opportunities weve searched the world for the most outstanding investment managers who can help your clients tap into the most exciting investment opportunities wherever they may be analytic global managed volatility fund global equities with low volatility aims to provide a lowvolatility and longterm global investment option  the fund offers the potential for consistent aboveindex returns over the long term and provides access to analytic a pioneer in quantitativelydriven lowvolatility equity investment management arrowstreet global equity fund longterm global equities exposure take a longterm approach to investing in global equities arrowstreets fund managers take an active quantitative investment approach that aims to add value through varying market conditions the fund invests in companies from developed and emerging markets macquarie offers unhedged and hedged versions of the fund ifp global franchise fund access to leading international brands ifps fund managers take a low turnover buyandhold approach to investing for the fund with a focus on value and capital preservation this means they only invest in approximately  to  high quality companies at a time and focus on businesses with high free cash flow and dominant intangible assets such as a brand patent or licences macquarie offers unhedged and hedged versions of the fund macquarie asia new stars no fund uncovering new opportunities in asia your clients can capitalise on the potential capital growth of small and midsized companies in the worlds most dynamic economic region the fund provides exposure to small to midsized businesses in asia excluding japan and aims to provide both capital growth and some income macquaries fund managers take a rigorous bottomup approach to selecting stock and identifying investments with low valuations and high growth potential polaris global equity fund access a diversified portfolio of valueoriented global equities provides exposure to a diversified portfolio of global equities that polaris believes are the most attractive value opportunities the fund is actively managed using a benchmarkunaware bottomup researchdriven approach with a focus on sustainable free cash flow it generally holds between  and  securities of globallylisted companies including those in emerging markets and small capitalisation companies walter scott emerging markets fund access growth companies in emerging markets help your clients access the highgrowth potential of companies in emerging markets walter scotts bottomup fundamental approach to investing focuses on companies from developing economies that offer longterm growth potential walter scotts experienced fund managers pay particular attention to factors such as strong earnings growth high return on equity and high free cash flow walter scott global equity fund highgrowth companies in global markets walter scott scours global markets for what it believes are the worlds best companies its fundamental bottomup investment approach combines detailed financial analysis with business and industry analysis your clients can benefit from walter scotts selective stock picking and ability to target companies capable of sustainable wealth generation macquarie offers unhedged and hedged versions of the fund about fixed income fixed income investments such as government and corporate bonds can provide regular income and capital growth for your clients and can help mitigate the risk of investing too heavily in one asset class macquarie has over  years of fixed income experience and can offer your clients some of what we believe are the best opportunities from around the world macquarie diversified fixed interest fund a defensive and multisector bond solution offers exposure to a diversified portfolio of fixed interest and creditbased investments macquaries fund managers aim to provide a regular income and some capital growth by actively identifying outperforming fixed interest and credit sectors the fund also minimises currency volatility through hedging macquarie income opportunities fund an income solution with a focus on preserving capital attempts to provide a regular income at a better rate of return than bank or term deposits by giving your clients exposure to interestbearing securities issued by a range of different companies the funds capital preservation focus means it invests in a diversified portfolio of highly liquid securities about alternatives governments and companies increasingly use private investment to fund large infrastructure projects such as roads airports and hospitals investing in this important asset class offers your clients the potential for stable inflationlinked income capital growth and portfolio diversification meanwhile our absolute return fund also has the potential to generate positive returns even in falling markets macquarie international infrastructure securities fund exposure to the global infrastructure assets offers your clients a global portfolio of listed infrastructure securities the fund invests across both developed and emerging markets as well as across infrastructure sectors investment decisions are only made after macquaries large specialist infrastructure team has conducted intensive fundamental research macquarie offers unhedged and hedged versions of the fund winton global alpha fund diversification to traditional portfolios aims to generate longterm returns for your clients through a specialised managed futures trading strategy with the potential to generate positive returns in both rising and falling markets the fund can provide valuable portfolio diversification benefits wintons investment teams modeldriven automated approach to trading involves analysing market trends and then developing mathematicallybased strategies to capitalise on them performance latest performance reports fund performance unit prices unit prices distribution information documents and forms product disclosure statements fatcacrs selfcertification form online registration form aml policy annual reports proxy voting information other forms view all tools expertise articles did you mean statesuggestion sorry stateerrormessage sorry no results found try different keywords expertise articles market insights investing in australian small companies market insights fixed income and currency things you should know market insights insights from asia market insights iron ore rising why the rally won’t be sustained view more articles find out how we can help if you’d like to speak to a macquarie business development manager about how we can help get in touch talk to macquarie macquarie investment management ltd company profile  bloomberg feedback macquarie investment management ltd private company company profile sector financials industry asset management subindustry investment management macquarie investment management ltd operates as an investment management company the company offers asset management trading funds money transfers investment strategies financial planning and advisory services macquarie investment management serves customers worldwide corporate information address  martin place sydney nsw  australia phone  fax  web url wwwmacqu